3. cs.CG (Computational Geometry) - The paper may be relevant to computational geometry as it deals with graph problems that can be represented geometrically. 
4. cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) - The paper may be relevant to game theory as feedback vertex sets are used in the analysis of games on graphs.
